assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: International Care Company S.p.A. provides digital health care services in Italy and internationally. It offers medical assistance services, including telephone medical consultation, home delivery of medicines, medical dispatch at home, sending pediatrician/cardiologist to home, second opinion, manages appointment of doctors via the operational center, online medical passport, and medical record translation services; and home assistance services, such as emergency locksmith and hydraulic dispatch, emergency dispatch electrician, pet assistance, veterinary advice, credit card blocking and replacement, and supervision and custody of assets, as well as services related to damage to the house, expenses for remaking documents, save documents, and sending craftsman for bricklayer, glazier, etc. The company also provides travel assistance services comprising ticket office and hotel accommodation, medical transport, early return, repatriation of the body, repetition of the trip, medical dispatch at home, medical consultation, home delivery of medicines, and babysitting services, as well as services related to advance expenses for basic necessities; and auto assistance services consisting of roadside assistance, repatriation of the vehicle, car replacement, sending driver or taxi, organization of the return trip, sending spare parts, hotel expenses, advance of money, mechanical dispatch, and ambulance transport. In addition, it offers telemonitoring service and video call with doctors, call and satellite centers, and claims management services. The company was founded in 2018 and is based in Agrate Brianza, Italy. International Care Company S.p.A. is a subsidiary of FD Holding S.p.A.
